Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest queue target

Purpose:
  Change the target stage of an existing active job.

Usage:
  spinedigest queue target <job-id> --to graph|summary

Arguments:
  <job-id>              Full job id or an unambiguous prefix.

Options:
  --to graph|summary    New target.

Rules:
  - Upgrading graph to summary is allowed while the job is active.
  - Downgrading summary to graph is allowed only before summary has started.
  - If summary has already started, cancel explicitly instead of downgrading.

Example:
  spinedigest queue target 75d12f7e --to summary
